Description: This package is intended as a boilerplate that prospective developers can use as a template to get started more rapidly.
    In particular, it provides code, man pages, vignettes, and unit tests,
    as well as GitHub Action workflows for continuous integration and continuous deployment of a Docker container and a pkgdown website on GitHub Pages.
